# Input

```svelte
{#each items as item, i (item.id)} <div>{i}: {item.name}</div> {:else} <div>Empty list</div> {/each}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#each items as item, i (item.id)}
	<div>{i}: {item.name}</div>
{:else}
	<div>Empty list</div>
{/each}

```
